name: Chevron Wrapping Paper
description:
3 Sheets of Chevron Wrapping Paper from the Swimmers Collection

Lithograph printed onto 

100gsm thick uncoated FSC Certified paper

50cm x 70cm 

Pen On Paper’s first range of wrapping paper came from some great patterns we made for our package labels and dancing couples too brilliant to stay out of the limelight. In three designs there’s plenty of choice - from simple but decorative patterns to dancing couples, there is a wrap for every occasion. 

Make a great first impression this Christmas with the best wrapped gifts under the tree, or better still, get us to wrap and deliver them straight to your loved ones! Just make sure your delivery address has the name of the lucky recipient and email us your personal message. Now hasn’t Christmas shopping just gotten a lot easier and stylish? You’re welcome.
